Package: wastdr
Type: Package
Title: WA Sea Turtle Database 'WAStD' API Wrapper
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(c("Florian", "W."), "Mayer", 
    email="Florian.Mayer@dpaw.wa.gov.au", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Florian W. Mayer [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Florian W. Mayer <Florian.Mayer@dpaw.wa.gov.au>
Description: The 'WA Sea Turtle Database' 'WAStD' is a 'Django' web app with a 'RESTful'
    'API' returning 'GeoJSON' 'FeatureCollections'. 'wastdr' provides helpers to retrieve
    data from the 'API', and to turn the received 'GeoJSON' into R 'tibbles'.
    'wastdr' will grow alongside implemented use cases of retrieving and analysing
    'WAStD' data.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    httr,
    jsonlite
Imports:
    lubridate,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tibble
Suggests:
    ckanr,
    DT,
    Hmisc,
    htmlTable,
    knitr,
    listviewer,
    plyr,
    rmarkdown,
    tidyverse,
    testthat
